      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="question-bank-overview" data-step-uuid="27222abd-756b-4464-9d8d-ee38555707a0">
    <h2 id="question-bank-overview" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Question Bank Overview</h2>
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_92ea2815-9fb3-46e1-9877-ecb91b728eb0" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Question banks are quiz question repositories. When creating a quiz, users can access question bank questions, making it easier to offer the same quiz questions to students in different courses.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-manage-question-banks-in-an-account/ta-p/231" target="_blank">How do I manage question banks in an account?</a></li>
